webSettings.setRenderPriority(WebSettings.RenderPriority.HIGH);
webSettings.setCacheMode(WebSettings.LOAD_CACHE_ELSE_NETWORK);
```

### 2. Memory Management
```java
@Override
protected void onDestroy() {
    if (webView != null) {
        webView.destroy();
        webView = null;
    }
    super.onDestroy();
}
```

## Security Considerations

### 1. HTTPS Only
```xml
<!-- Force HTTPS in production -->
<domain-config cleartextTrafficPermitted="false">
    <domain includeSubdomains="true">your-production-url.com</domain>
</domain-config>
```

### 2. Content Security Policy
```java
// Add CSP headers
webSettings.setMixedContentMode(WebSettings.MIXED_CONTENT_COMPATIBILITY_MODE);
```

## Troubleshooting

### 1. Common Issues
- **White screen**: Check internet permission and URL
- **File upload not working**: Enable file access permissions
- **JavaScript errors**: Ensure JavaScript is enabled

### 2. Debug Mode
```java
// Enable debugging
if (BuildConfig.DEBUG) {
    WebView.setWebContentsDebuggingEnabled(true);
}
```

